  {
    icon: '📐',
    title: 'Qualifies Chimney Problem Types',
    text: "Through conversation, the AI identifies whether the visitor has a damp investigation, a structural repair, a flue lining need, a breast removal project, or a pot and cowl issue. You receive a categorised lead matched to your capability."
  },
  {
    icon: '🕐',
    title: 'Converts Evening Damp Research',
    text: "Rain starts at 8pm. By 9pm a homeowner spots the brown stain spreading on the bedroom chimney breast. By 10pm she is on your website searching 'chimney damp specialist.' Chat captures her urgency while she stares at the stain."
  },
  {
    icon: '📊',
