  {
    icon: '🔗',
    title: 'Works Alongside Chimney Case Studies',
    text: "Your website shows before-and-after chimney rebuilds, lime mortar repointing close-ups, and flue lining installations. Chat converts visitors studying your completed chimney work into booked inspections."
